Package JWordle

Interface Enter

All Known Implementing Classes:
ButtonOperator, KeyboardReader
public interface Enter
The Enter interface judges a line of letter reference a wordlist.

This interface has only one static method submit. Components which implements this interface can check whether a line of word is in the wordlist and change the letter color to gray, green, yellow correspond to letter not in answer, letter in the correct place, letter in the wrong place via static method submit.

This interface is the ONLY WAY to change theme in the SingleBox instance.
